headline: Why Generac (GNRC) Shares Are Sliding Today
summary: Shares of power generation products company Generac (NYSE:GNRC) fell 3% in the afternoon session after Citigroup downgraded the stock's rating to 'Neutral' from 'Buy', citing valuation concerns.
